IF EXIST %BOOMDIR%\BOOM.EXE IF NOT EXIST BOOM\SCRNCAP\DOOM*.PCX ECHO.

REM Installation check in case the installation is not found
IF NOT EXIST %BOOMDIR%\BOOM.EXE ECHO BOOM: Installation not found. Skipping...
